sentences.content: Scene narratives let the user describe complex scenes by decomposing it into simpler subscenes.
Going to get a haircut
The man is wearing a yellow shirt and jeans.
He is stepping onto the sidewalk from the street.
Finding Ann's hair salon
The storefront has large glass windows.
The front door is red.
A welcome mat sits in front of the door.
Getting a haircut
The hair stylist is wearing a yellow dress.
She is cutting a woman's long hair.
Waiting for a haircut
Another man is waiting.
He is wearing an orange shirt.
He is reading a magazine.
